trans-unit.source: Represents a response of a <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma resposta de um <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: When you use the pack URI protocol, you can reference a package and its part elements either locally from inside a package or externally from a Web source.
trans-unit.target: Quando utiliza o protocolo URI do pacote, pode referenciar um pacote e os respetivos elementos parte a localmente a partir do dentro de um pacote ou externamente a partir de uma origem de Web.

trans-unit.source: For the pack URI protocol, the forward-slash characters (//) of an embedded [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] are represented by commas (,,).
trans-unit.target: Para o pacote de protocolo URI, os carateres de reencaminhamento barra (/ /) de um embedded [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] são representados por vírgulas (,).

trans-unit.source: For example: `pack://http:,,www.adatum.com,folder,file.package/images/picture1.jpg` references the file `/images/picture1.jpg` that is contained in `http://www.adatum.com/folder/file.package`.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo: `pack://http:,,www.adatum.com,folder,file.package/images/picture1.jpg` referencia o ficheiro `/images/picture1.jpg` que está contida no `http://www.adatum.com/folder/file.package`.

trans-unit.source: Closes the stream for this request.
trans-unit.target: Fecha a sequência para este pedido.

trans-unit.source: Make certain that objects close when they are no longer in use so that resources are not exhausted.
trans-unit.target: Certifique-se de que os objetos fechar quando já não estão em utilização para que os recursos não ficam esgotados.

trans-unit.source: Gets the content length of the response.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o comprimento do conteúdo da resposta.

trans-unit.source: The content length, in bytes.
trans-unit.target: O comprimento do conteúdo, em bytes.

trans-unit.source: Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-mime-md.md)] content type of the response stream's content.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-mime-md.md)] tipo de conteúdo de fluxo de respostas de conteúdo.

trans-unit.source: If a request does not specify a part in the package, it returns the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] type of the package.
trans-unit.target: Se um pedido de especificar uma parte do pacote, devolve a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] tipo do pacote.

trans-unit.source: Requests that specify a part in the package return one of the following: 1.
trans-unit.target: Pedidos que especifiquem uma parte no pacote de devolverem um dos seguintes: 1.

trans-unit.source: If the requested part contains a <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A> value, the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A> value is returned.
trans-unit.target: Se a parte do pedido contém um <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>valor, o <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>valor é devolvido.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the requested part contains no <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A> value but the stream name contains a recognized [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] extension type, the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] type corresponding to the extension is returned.
trans-unit.target: Se a parte do pedido contém não <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>valor, mas o nome do fluxo contém um reconhecido [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] tipo de extensão, a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] devolveu o tipo correspondente para a extensão.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the requested part does not contain a <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A> value nor a recognized [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] extension type, ContentType returns an empty string.
trans-unit.target: Se a parte do pedido não contém um <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>valor nem um reconhecido [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] tipo de extensão, ContentType devolve uma cadeia vazia.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] type of the stream's content.
trans-unit.target: O [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] tipo de conteúdo no fluxo.

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: A adicionar.

trans-unit.source: Gets the response stream that is contained in the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a sequência de resposta que faz a <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The response stream.
trans-unit.target: Fluxo de respostas.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of Web <xref:System.Net.WebResponse.Headers*> for this response.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a coleção de Web <xref:System.Net.WebResponse.Headers*>para esta resposta.</xref:System.Net.WebResponse.Headers*>

trans-unit.source: The collection of Web response <xref:System.Net.WebResponse.Headers*>.
trans-unit.target: A recolha de respostas da Web <xref:System.Net.WebResponse.Headers*>.</xref:System.Net.WebResponse.Headers*>

trans-unit.source: Gets the inner <xref:System.Net.WebResponse> object for the response.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a interna <xref:System.Net.WebResponse>objeto para a resposta.</xref:System.Net.WebResponse>

trans-unit.source: InnerResponse returns `null` when the response is from the package cache (when <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse.IsFromCache%2A> is `true`).
trans-unit.target: Devolve InnerResponse `null` quando a resposta é da cache do pacote (quando <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse.IsFromCache%2A>é `true`).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse.IsFromCache%2A>

trans-unit.source: The response data as a <xref:System.Net.WebResponse>.
trans-unit.target: Os dados da resposta como <xref:System.Net.WebResponse>.</xref:System.Net.WebResponse>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the response is from the package cache or from a Web request.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se a resposta é a partir da cache do pacote ou a partir de um pedido Web.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the response is from the package cache; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if the response is from a Web request.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Se a resposta da cache do pacote; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> se a resposta é um pedido Web.

trans-unit.source: Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] of the response.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] da resposta.

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the response.
trans-unit.target: O [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] da resposta.
